# f5distributedcloud_bgp_asn_set (Resource)

The `f5distributedcloud_bgp_asn_set` resource manages BGP ASN Sets in F5 Distributed Cloud.

BGP ASN Sets define collections of Autonomous System Numbers for BGP routing policies.

## Example Usage

```hcl
resource "f5distributedcloud_bgp_asn_set" "example" {
  name        = "my-asn-set"
  namespace   = "system"
  description = "BGP ASN set for routing"
  asns        = [65000, 65001, 65002]
}
```

## Schema

### Required

- `name` (String)
- `namespace` (String)

### Optional

- `asns` (List of Number) List of Autonomous System Numbers.
- `description` (String)

### Read-Only

- `id` (String) The ID of this resource.
